comments: The survey went well. Thank you for allowing me to participate.

I enjoyed the survey thank you.
none at this time. Have a great day!

no thank you for the opportunity

This was interesting and took less than 20 minutes to complete when reading thoroughly and paying full attention
Sometimes I am more satisfied with an interaction when I contribute more to the relationship. It helps me feel more invested in it.

I feel like overall I understood the instructions and how to "rate" each scenario. However, reading the prompt, then the two scenarios and the after that to rate two different outcomes, that was a bit confusing and hard t keep track of who was who and how the two groups were different or not from one another.
I feel like the questions were very open ended and left a lot up to interpretation. But I assume that is how this study was intended.
